RE: REVISED March 28th Power Marketing Conference Call

This week's Power Marketers Working Group conference call will be held on 
Wednesday, March 28th, at 2:00 p.m. (EST).  To access the call, dial
1-800-937-6563.  Ask for the Julie Simon/EPSA Call.  We inadvertently deleted 
the FERC agenda items from the agenda forwarded earlier, so a revised agenda 
is outlined below.

